**[Dark Souls III](/dark-souls-iii) Any% Glitchless** is a speedrun category in which the player tries to complete the game as fast as possible.\
\
The use of glitches is not allowed in this category.

## Getting Started

- Visit the **[Getting Started](/darksouls3/getting-started)** page for information on how to get started with **[Dark Souls III](/dark-souls-iii)** speedrunning.
- Visit the **[Rules](/darksouls3/rules)** page to find the rules for speedrunning **[Dark Souls III](/dark-souls-iii)**
- Visit the **[Routes](/darksouls3/routes)** page to find available route notes for different speedrun categories of **[Dark Souls III](/dark-souls-iii)**

